### Telegram Bot Commands

    /start
    /health
    /task

Example:

    /task Проанализируй материалы клиента

------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Backend Endpoints

    GET /health
    POST /tasks

Example request:

``` json
{
  "input_text": "..."
}
```

Example response:

``` json
{
"id": "uuid",
"text": "test",
"status": "created"
}
```

